Detects the Scanner from the filename.

Based on the script by perezmu

Authors: Perezmu, Stonepaw, 600WPMPO, Helmic


How to use:
Just double-click the crplugin file to install it into ComicRack.
Select the book(s), whose scanner name you wish to import into the Scan Information field.
Right-click, and from the Automation menu, click at 'Scan Information From Filename'

Alternatively, select the desired books, and simply click at the icon on the browser toolbar:
